  <summary date="2021-02-05T20:08:07Z" status="Introduced in House">21st Century SCRA Act

This bill specifies that a service member who is authorized under current law to terminate a lease of premises or a motor vehicle lease without incurring an early termination fee may provide notice of the termination by electronic delivery to an email address designated by the lessor or the lessor's agent.</summary>
